          Integrated financial, digital, and business services. All operations
          are monitored. Southbag assumes no liability for consequential losses
          arising from service availability, policy enforcement, or compliance
          holds.
        </p>
        <div class="sb-footer-reg">
          <span class="sb-label">Reg. No.</span>
          <span
            class="sb-mono"
            style="font-size:11px;color:var(--sb-text-dimmer)"
            >SB-INS-00-1924</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sb-footer-col">
        <div class="sb-footer-col-head">Financial</div>
        <ul class="sb-footer-links">
          <li><a href="/financial">Online Banking</a></li>
          <li><a href="/financial">Invest</a></li>
          <li><a href="/financial">Crypto Exchange</a></li>
          <li><a href="/financial">Pay Later</a></li>
          <li><a href="/financial">Tax</a></li>
          <li><a href="/financial">Insurance</a></li>
          <li><a href="/financial">Compliance</a></li>
          <li><a href="/financial">Payroll</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sb-footer-col">
        <div class="sb-footer-col-head">Digital</div>
        <ul class="sb-footer-links">
          <li><a href="/digital">Broadband</a></li>
          <li><a href="/digital">Mobile</a></li>
          <li><a href="/digital">Firewall</a></li>
          <li><a href="/digital">VPN</a></li>
          <li><a href="/digital">Code</a></li>
          <li><a href="/digital">AI</a></li>
          <li><a href="/digital">DNS</a></li>
          <li><a href="/digital">CSS</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sb-footer-col">
        <div class="sb-footer-col-head">Business</div>
        <ul class="sb-footer-links">
          <li><a href="/business">Secure Access</a></li>
          <li><a href="/business">MDM</a></li>
          <li><a href="/business">CRM</a></li>
          <li><a href="/business">Version Control</a></li>
          <li><a href="/business">Data Lake</a></li>
          <li><a href="/business">Analytics</a></li>
          <li><a href="/business">Edge Compute</a></li>
          <li><a href="/business">Ecommerce</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sb-footer-col">
        <div class="sb-footer-col-head">Legal &amp; Policy</div>
        <ul class="sb-footer-links">
          <li><a href="#">Terms of Service</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Acceptable Use</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Data Residency</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Compliance Framework</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Appeals Process</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Kevin: Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sb-footer-bottom">
      <div class="sb-footer-bottom-left">
        <span>© {currentYear} Southbag Institutional Services Ltd.</span>
        <span class="sb-footer-sep">·</span>
        <span>All rights reserved.</span>
        <span class="sb-footer-sep">·</span>
        <span>All policy decisions are final and reviewed by Kevin.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sb-footer-bottom-right">
        <span class="sb-kevin sb-kevin-reviewed">Reviewed by Kevin</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .sb-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--sb-border);
    background: var(--sb-surface);
    margin-top: 80px;
  }

  .sb-footer-inner {
    padding-top: 56px;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .sb-footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sb-border);
  }

  .sb-footer-wordmark {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: var(--sb-heading);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .sb-footer-tagline {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--sb-text-dimmer);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    max-width: 280px;
  }

  .sb-footer-reg {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .sb-footer-col-head {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sb-text-dimmer);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sb-border);
  }

  .sb-footer-links {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .sb-footer-links a {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--sb-text-dimmer);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }

  .sb-footer-links a:hover {
    color: var(--sb-text);
  }

  .sb-footer-bottom {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 16px 0;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .sb-footer-bottom-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--sb-text-dimmer);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .sb-footer-sep {
    color: var(--sb-border-hover);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .sb-footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .sb-footer-brand {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .sb-footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .sb-footer-brand {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
  }
</style>
